profile:
Brantford Lock & Security Co. is the right choice when it comes to safety & security in Brantford, ON. We specialize in lock installations for residential and commercial properties. Contact us today!

Brantford Lock & Security Co. offers mobile locksmith services in Brantford. Our professional locksmiths are trained in residential, commercial and industrial lock services. We cater to lock sales & installation, lockout service for homes, businesses & vehicles, lock rekeying and security alarm systems. We deal in master key systems, high-security deadbolts, lock combination change, as well as doors and window bars. You can trust us with the installation of metal doors. Book your appointment.
project_minimum: No job is too small or big
